    "It was decided to use a multiclass SVM in the CADx system because it can find the best hyperplanes for separating classes with the most space, even when classes are closely related 34, 35.",
    "The SVM is a reliable way to find the stages of colorectal cancer in the PolynetDWTCADx system because it uses class distinction well in either one-vs-one or one-vs-all approaches.",
    "Integrated CNN + DWT CNNs are capable of recognizing colorectal abnormalities by learning the deep-level features of any image acquired during a colonoscopy and identifying details that are essential for this purpose.",
    "By adding this element to DWT, it will be easier to separate the image into frequency bands that capture changes in both space and time, which will improve feature extraction.",
